name: Feed Me Genes
description:
Simple small game for ScoreSpace Jam #24 🕹️.

Click on the genes that correspond to the color on the top left, a voice will also indicate that color so you don't need to look away.

If you liked the game, you can check out  my other games on Steam:  https://store.steampowered.com/developer/guilemus
